name: Love Will Be Reborn | Video Fragment 04
description:
This is one of five shots created for Martha Wainwright's, Love Will Be Reborn,
music video available as an NFT. You can see the full video here https://youtu.be/9Fj5DOhqYlA  Huge thanks & respect to Martha and her record label for allowing us to release our work from the video as NFTs. This NFT contains the visuals only and not the music.
